span_gcd:
theorem span_gcd {α} [EuclideanDomain α] (x y : α) : span ({gcd x y} : set α) = span ({x, y} : set α) :=
  letI := euclidean_domain.gcd_monoid α
  span_gcd x y
#align span_gcd span_gcd
right_div_gcd_ne_zero:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Tactic/Lean3.lean:132:4: warning: unsupported: rw with cfg: { occs := occurrences.pos[occurrences.pos] «expr[ ,]»([1]) } -/
theorem right_div_gcd_ne_zero {p q : R} (hq : q ≠ 0) : q / gcd_monoid.gcd p q ≠ 0 :=
  by
  obtain ⟨r, hr⟩ := gcd_monoid.gcd_dvd_right p q
  obtain ⟨pq0, r0⟩ : gcd_monoid.gcd p q ≠ 0 ∧ r ≠ 0 := mul_ne_zero_iff.mp (hr ▸ hq)
  rw [hr, mul_comm, mul_div_cancel _ pq0]
  exact r0
#align right_div_gcd_ne_zero right_div_gcd_ne_zero

theorem left_div_gcd_ne_zero {p q : R} (hp : p ≠ 0) : p / gcd_monoid.gcd p q ≠ 0 :=

  obtain ⟨r, hr⟩ := gcd_monoid.gcd_dvd_left p q

is_coprime_of_dvd:
-- this should be proved for UFDs surely?
theorem is_coprime_of_dvd {α} [EuclideanDomain α] {x y : α} (nonzero : ¬(x = 0 ∧ y = 0))
    (H : ∀ z ∈ nonunits α, z ≠ 0 → z ∣ x → ¬z ∣ y) : IsCoprime x y :=
  letI := euclidean_domain.gcd_monoid α
  is_coprime_of_dvd x y nonzero H
#align is_coprime_of_dvd is_coprime_of_dvd
gcd_ne_zero_of_right:
theorem gcd_ne_zero_of_right (p q : R) (hp : q ≠ 0) : gcd_monoid.gcd p q ≠ 0 := fun h =>
  hp <| eq_zero_of_zero_dvd (h ▸ gcd_dvd_right p q)
#align gcd_ne_zero_of_right gcd_ne_zero_of_right

gcd_is_unit_iff:
theorem gcd_is_unit_iff {α} [EuclideanDomain α] {x y : α} : is_unit (gcd x y) ↔ IsCoprime x y :=
  letI := euclidean_domain.gcd_monoid α
  gcd_is_unit_iff x y
#align gcd_is_unit_iff gcd_is_unit_iff
dvd_or_coprime:
-- this should be proved for UFDs surely?
theorem dvd_or_coprime {α} [EuclideanDomain α] (x y : α) (h : Irreducible x) : x ∣ y ∨ IsCoprime x y :=
  letI := euclidean_domain.gcd_monoid α
  dvd_or_coprime x y h
#align dvd_or_coprime dvd_or_coprime
